snippet.title: Tuned Turtle - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Tuned Turtle is a wacky 2D Platformer based on the Tortoise x Hare fable 🐢 x 🐇 

Tune up your shell with mighty unlockable power-ups (like baseball thrower, power armor) and cross the finish line before Loko Rabbit

Wishlist this adventure on Steam:
tunedturtle.com/steam

Follow us
instagram.com/tunedturtle
twitter.com/tunedturtle
